      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values practicality, affordability, and the opportunity to own a vehicle without a major upfront investment. A sensible choice for commuting, backup use, or a project-minded owner looking for solid value.",
