    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runabout with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece and does have the wear you\u2019d expect, but it starts, moves, and could make a handy budget commuter, project, or spare vehicle. If you\u2019re after something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and open to sensible interest.",
      "price": 4900.0,
