    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of old-school presence that turns a simple drive into a story. It\u2019s a gritty, honest machine with plenty of character, ideal for someone who sees potential where others see a weekend project. Whether you\u2019re after an affordable driver to tinker with, a platform for a creative build, or just something with real personality, this one brings charm that can\u2019t be faked. A hands-on buyer will appreciate the chance to make it their own and enjoy the journey along the way.",
      "price": 7900.0,
